{
  "id": "2021-09-30_screen_english",
  "date": "2021-09-30",
  "corner": "screen_english",
  "corner_label": "Screen English",
  "title": "Sorry for interrupting",
  "movie": "",
  "duration_sec": 728.8,
  "audio_url": "https://rtyzdyyfahddqshgyjvn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/gmp-audio/2021-09-30_screen_english.mp3",
  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 34.41,
      "text": "영화배달 서비스 스크린 잉글리쉬 타임"
    },
    {
      "start": 34.41,
      "end": 36.37,
      "text": "9월에 함께하고 있는 영화는"
    },
    {
      "start": 36.37,
      "end": 39.23,
      "text": "It's about a hearing girl who wants to sing"
    },
    {
      "start": 39.23,
      "end": 43.15,
      "text": "but she has deaf parents who rely on her to integrate"
    },
    {
      "start": 43.15,
      "end": 44.93,
      "text": "and they always have"
    },
    {
      "start": 44.93,
      "end": 46.63,
      "text": "Yes, they always have"
    },
    {
      "start": 46.63,
      "end": 47.29,
      "text": "CODA!"
    },
    {
      "start": 47.45,
      "end": 50.61,
      "text": "와우! 영화같이 멋지게 등장하셨습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 50.87,
      "end": 51.79,
      "text": "Hello! Good morning!"
    },
    {
      "start": 51.95,
      "end": 53.59,
      "text": "임선화 님께서"
    },
    {
      "start": 53.59,
      "end": 57.71,
      "text": "조크쌤 케미는 항상 아침에 즐거운 기운을 선사해요."
    },
    {
      "start": 57.83,
      "end": 59.37,
      "text": "웃음 웃음 감사합니다. 웃음 웃음"
    },
    {
      "start": 59.37,
      "end": 61.79,
      "text": "오늘도 족쌤과 함께"
    },
    {
      "start": 61.79,
      "end": 62.95,
      "text": "Let's go!"
    },
    {
      "start": 63.01,
      "end": 65.75,
      "text": "오늘도 한번 케미 뿜뿜 해보도록 하겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 65.89,
      "end": 66.37,
      "text": "뿜뿜뿜뿜"
    },
    {
      "start": 66.37,
      "end": 70.51,
      "text": "Anyway, I can tell it's one of the best movies of the year."
    },
    {
      "start": 70.71,
      "end": 72.55,
      "text": "Honestly, I loved it."
    },
    {
      "start": 72.75,
      "end": 73.75,
      "text": "I'm honest."
    },
    {
      "start": 73.97,
      "end": 75.41,
      "text": "I'm being completely honest."
    },
    {
      "start": 75.49,
      "end": 79.21,
      "text": "진짜 진심을 가득 담아가지고 표현을 해주고 계시네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 79.37,
      "end": 82.01,
      "text": "이 CODA의 영화에 감동을 참 많이 받았는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 82.01,
      "end": 85.91,
      "text": "이 영화는 features a number of classic songs"
    },
    {
      "start": 85.91,
      "end": 91.41,
      "text": "including pieces by Joni Mitchell, Marvin Gaye, and David Bowie."
    },
    {
      "start": 91.55,
      "end": 95.33,
      "text": "Yeah, many songs that many Koreans will be familiar with."
    },
    {
      "start": 95.51,
      "end": 96.89,
      "text": "Classic pop songs."
    },
    {
      "start": 97.71,
      "end": 99.93,
      "text": "Also, my wife, when she heard"
    },
    {
      "start": 99.93,
      "end": 102.41,
      "text": "you know the last song in the movie?"
    },
    {
      "start": 102.53,
      "end": 103.65,
      "text": "The Audition."
    },
    {
      "start": 103.85,
      "end": 106.43,
      "text": "Yeah, Both Sides Now is the title of the song."
    },
    {
      "start": 106.43,
      "end": 108.39,
      "text": "Both Sides Now by Joni Mitchell."
    },
    {
      "start": 108.61,
      "end": 109.85,
      "text": "That was beautiful."
    },
    {
      "start": 109.85,
      "end": 112.45,
      "text": "It was actually my first time to hear that song."
    },
    {
      "start": 112.95,
      "end": 113.71,
      "text": "But my wife said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 113.79,
      "end": 115.11,
      "text": "어디서 들었지?"
    },
    {
      "start": 115.47,
      "end": 119.35,
      "text": "She remembered, she heard that song from a commercial,"
    },
    {
      "start": 119.67,
      "end": 121.29,
      "text": "an old commercial in Korea"
    },
    {
      "start": 121.29,
      "end": 123.39,
      "text": "for a clothing brand"
    },
    {
      "start": 123.39,
      "end": 125.11,
      "text": "with Daniel Henney"
    },
    {
      "start": 125.11,
      "end": 127.77,
      "text": "and Paltrow,"
    },
    {
      "start": 128.17,
      "end": 128.91,
      "text": "Gwyneth Paltrow,"
    },
    {
      "start": 129.09,
      "end": 130.37,
      "text": "the famous actress."
    },
    {
      "start": 130.57,
      "end": 131.71,
      "text": "They did a commercial,"
    },
    {
      "start": 132.07,
      "end": 134.49,
      "text": "a clothing commercial for a famous Korean brand."
    },
    {
      "start": 134.49,
      "end": 138.69,
      "text": "Daniel Henney가 나와서 더 인상 깊게 음악을 들으신 게 아닐까?"
    },
    {
      "start": 139.85,
      "end": 140.37,
      "text": "No."
    },
    {
      "start": 141.17,
      "end": 142.61,
      "text": "Well, 이제 안 좋아요, 이제."
    },
    {
      "start": 143.41,
      "end": 143.95,
      "text": "아무튼."
    },
    {
      "start": 144.07,
      "end": 145.27,
      "text": "아무튼 거기서 나갔대요."
    },
    {
      "start": 145.31,
      "end": 145.55,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 146.09,
      "end": 146.99,
      "text": "그러면 크리스 씨네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 147.07,
      "end": 149.65,
      "text": "What's the most memorable song out of the OST?"
    },
    {
      "start": 149.99,
      "end": 151.23,
      "text": "It was that song"
    },
    {
      "start": 151.23,
      "end": 152.49,
      "text": "until you mentioned"
    },
    {
      "start": 152.49,
      "end": 153.79,
      "text": "Daniel Henney."
    },
    {
      "start": 153.95,
      "end": 155.53,
      "text": "저도 마찬가지로."
    },
    {
      "start": 155.67,
      "end": 156.29,
      "text": "I like that."
    },
    {
      "start": 156.35,
      "end": 156.55,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 157.15,
      "end": 158.25,
      "text": "이 Both Sides Now"
    },
    {
      "start": 158.25,
      "end": 160.95,
      "text": "라는 곡을 가장 인상 깊게 들었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 161.17,
      "end": 161.91,
      "text": "It was touching."
    },
    {
      "start": 161.91,
      "end": 162.35,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 162.77,
      "end": 165.47,
      "text": "특히 그 마지막 오디션 장면에서"
    },
    {
      "start": 165.47,
      "end": 168.63,
      "text": "이 곡을 불렀었던 장면이 있었습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 168.77,
      "end": 169.49,
      "text": "And her family,"
    },
    {
      "start": 169.59,
      "end": 172.51,
      "text": "my favorite part was when her family came in the audition room."
    },
    {
      "start": 172.57,
      "end": 173.03,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "start": 173.35,
      "end": 174.35,
      "text": "They were on the balcony."
    },
    {
      "start": 174.59,
      "end": 175.09,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 175.17,
      "end": 176.17,
      "text": "And they were watching her."
    },
    {
      "start": 176.17,
      "end": 178.75,
      "text": "So she started sign language,"
    },
    {
      "start": 178.95,
      "end": 180.53,
      "text": "doing sign language while singing."
    },
    {
      "start": 180.77,
      "end": 182.15,
      "text": "And the judges were like,"
    },
    {
      "start": 182.21,
      "end": 183.15,
      "text": "Who's here?"
    },
    {
      "start": 183.33,
      "end": 183.99,
      "text": "What's happening?"
    },
    {
      "start": 184.25,
      "end": 185.37,
      "text": "But she didn't care."
    },
    {
      "start": 185.45,
      "end": 186.05,
      "text": "눈치 안 보고."
    },
    {
      "start": 186.23,
      "end": 186.51,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 186.61,
      "end": 187.79,
      "text": "She was trying to,"
    },
    {
      "start": 187.89,
      "end": 188.67,
      "text": "that was her love."
    },
    {
      "start": 188.81,
      "end": 190.41,
      "text": "She was showing love for her parents."
    },
    {
      "start": 190.49,
      "end": 190.73,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "start": 190.83,
      "end": 192.53,
      "text": "For bringing her all the way to this audition."
    },
    {
      "start": 192.67,
      "end": 195.45,
      "text": "Oh, 그래서 I couldn't help crying in that scene."
    },
    {
      "start": 195.79,
      "end": 197.05,
      "text": "I shed some tears too."
    },
    {
      "start": 197.15,
      "end": 198.93,
      "text": "저도 엄청 울었어요, 그 장면에서."
    },
    {
      "start": 199.03,
      "end": 199.31,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 199.31,
      "end": 201.01,
      "text": "가슴을 막 부여잡고 울었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 201.67,
      "end": 202.75,
      "text": "It really got to me."
    },
    {
      "start": 202.97,
      "end": 203.89,
      "text": "It hit you too."
    },
    {
      "start": 204.05,
      "end": 204.35,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 204.71,
      "end": 208.37,
      "text": "모두가 하나가 되는 그런 장면이 아니지 않나 싶습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 208.55,
      "end": 208.87,
      "text": "Beautiful."
    },
    {
      "start": 209.33,
      "end": 211.15,
      "text": "네, 먼저 이 장면 듣고 오겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 211.15,
      "end": 212.39,
      "text": "All right."
    },
    {
      "start": 212.73,
      "end": 214.73,
      "text": "You are just going to have to sing an acapella."
    },
    {
      "start": 217.33,
      "end": 218.43,
      "text": "I can accompany her."
    },
    {
      "start": 218.95,
      "end": 219.91,
      "text": "Sorry for interrupting."
    },
    {
      "start": 220.71,
      "end": 220.89,
      "text": "Hi."
    },
    {
      "start": 221.82,
      "end": 222.54,
      "text": "How are you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 223.34,
      "end": 225.14,
      "text": "I'm Bernardo Villalobos."
    },
    {
      "start": 225.88,
      "end": 226.56,
      "text": "Class of 89."
    },
    {
      "start": 227.58,
      "end": 228.42,
      "text": "Nice to see you all."
    },
    {
      "start": 229.27,
      "end": 229.89,
      "text": "May I?"
    },
    {
      "start": 230.65,
      "end": 231.35,
      "text": "I guess so."
    },
    {
      "start": 231.49,
      "end": 232.31,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "start": 232.73,
      "end": 234.59,
      "text": "What's going on?"
    },
    {
      "start": 240.42,
      "end": 248.96,
      "text": "That's the song."
    },
    {
      "start": 249.08,
      "end": 253.54,
      "text": "Yeah, dramatically her family sent her to the audition."
    },
    {
      "start": 254.16,
      "end": 254.8,
      "text": "They did."
    },
    {
      "start": 254.9,
      "end": 255.2,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 255.36,
      "end": 257.42,
      "text": "I didn't think they were going to."
    },
    {
      "start": 257.42,
      "end": 259.6,
      "text": "저도 전혀 예상하지 못했어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 260.0,
      "end": 263.92,
      "text": "가족들이 막판에 오디션에 보내게 됩니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 264.06,
      "end": 265.0,
      "text": "At the last minute."
    },
    {
      "start": 265.16,
      "end": 265.36,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 265.48,
      "end": 267.26,
      "text": "Okay, we're taking you to the audition."
    },
    {
      "start": 267.6,
      "end": 270.42,
      "text": "그리고 그 과정에서 her brother 있잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 270.42,
      "end": 272.92,
      "text": "wholeheartedly supported her."
    },
    {
      "start": 273.6,
      "end": 277.94,
      "text": "Ruby의 오빠가 바닷가에서 내가 너를 응원해."
    },
    {
      "start": 278.16,
      "end": 279.4,
      "text": "너 정말 재능이 있잖아."
    },
    {
      "start": 279.62,
      "end": 284.4,
      "text": "라고 하면서 격려해 주고 하는 부분이 참 nice scene이었다고 생각합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 284.4,
      "end": 290.2,
      "text": "Yeah, at first she was angry that she was going to give up her dream and stay with the family."
    },
    {
      "start": 290.34,
      "end": 291.46,
      "text": "We don't need you."
    },
    {
      "start": 291.7,
      "end": 292.3,
      "text": "Just go."
    },
    {
      "start": 292.3,
      "end": 292.38,
      "text": "Oh."
    },
    {
      "start": 292.76,
      "end": 298.54,
      "text": "근데 가족들이 역시 최고라는 생각을 하게 되는 연결이었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 298.54,
      "end": 298.78,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 298.8,
      "end": 299.32,
      "text": "역시 가족."
    },
    {
      "start": 299.68,
      "end": 300.4,
      "text": "가족이 힘."
    },
    {
      "start": 300.52,
      "end": 300.72,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 301.48,
      "end": 302.96,
      "text": "자, 표현들 점검해 볼까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 303.6,
      "end": 305.2,
      "text": "Sing it, acapella."
    },
    {
      "start": 305.58,
      "end": 307.46,
      "text": "Sing it, acapella."
    },
    {
      "start": 307.54,
      "end": 309.18,
      "text": "Acapella is one word, I think."
    },
    {
      "start": 309.2,
      "end": 309.44,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 309.66,
      "end": 310.22,
      "text": "Acapella."
    },
    {
      "start": 310.48,
      "end": 313.7,
      "text": "그런데 제가 궁금해가지고 사전도 찾아봤는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 313.7,
      "end": 316.62,
      "text": "진짜 A가 띄어져 있더라고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 317.34,
      "end": 318.46,
      "text": "아capella, 이렇게."
    },
    {
      "start": 318.72,
      "end": 319.3,
      "text": "아capella."
    },
    {
      "start": 319.66,
      "end": 321.76,
      "text": "Many times it's written as one word."
    },
    {
      "start": 321.8,
      "end": 322.28,
      "text": "그러니까요."
    },
    {
      "start": 322.34,
      "end": 325.48,
      "text": "마치 고유명사처럼 아capella 이렇게 붙어 있을 것 같은데"
    },
    {
      "start": 325.48,
      "end": 327.04,
      "text": "띄어져서 쓰이더라고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 327.04,
      "end": 330.26,
      "text": "Do you like to sing acapella or accompanied?"
    },
    {
      "start": 330.9,
      "end": 332.88,
      "text": "I've never done it before."
    },
    {
      "start": 333.34,
      "end": 334.6,
      "text": "Oh, you've done it here."
    },
    {
      "start": 334.94,
      "end": 336.14,
      "text": "When we talk and I say,"
    },
    {
      "start": 336.2,
      "end": 337.14,
      "text": "Hey, what's that song?"
    },
    {
      "start": 337.32,
      "end": 338.84,
      "text": "You sing a little bit acapella."
    },
    {
      "start": 338.96,
      "end": 339.44,
      "text": "그러네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 339.74,
      "end": 340.94,
      "text": "멀리 있지 않았네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 341.08,
      "end": 341.84,
      "text": "저도 했었네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 341.96,
      "end": 342.88,
      "text": "그것도 아capella예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 343.32,
      "end": 343.86,
      "text": "어, 그래요."
    },
    {
      "start": 344.0,
      "end": 344.5,
      "text": "무반주."
    },
    {
      "start": 344.64,
      "end": 345.92,
      "text": "무반주로 노래하다."
    },
    {
      "start": 346.18,
      "end": 347.7,
      "text": "아, 이렇게 와닿는 설명."
    },
    {
      "start": 347.86,
      "end": 348.26,
      "text": "감사합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 349.48,
      "end": 350.94,
      "text": "Sorry for interrupting."
    },
    {
      "start": 351.2,
      "end": 352.86,
      "text": "Sorry for interrupting."
    },
    {
      "start": 353.24,
      "end": 354.74,
      "text": "방해해서 죄송합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 354.74,
      "end": 356.42,
      "text": "라는 의미로 쓰입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 356.58,
      "end": 357.66,
      "text": "I'm so sorry for interrupting,"
    },
    {
      "start": 357.88,
      "end": 359.94,
      "text": "but I have something to say to you."
    },
    {
      "start": 360.04,
      "end": 360.26,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 360.26,
      "end": 363.68,
      "text": "뭔가 진짜 이야기하고 싶은 내용은 뒤에 따르기 마련이죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 364.18,
      "end": 365.82,
      "text": "Class of 89."
    },
    {
      "start": 366.1,
      "end": 367.4,
      "text": "A long time ago."
    },
    {
      "start": 367.54,
